ebdd245ca4f8807485ba8fc770095f390d4a0eeaee97267c0cd9b97d57e770d123be5dc7aac36abf9c5b1061cefbc7c383d9a0d48c341ceba9c880597ac6baa2  fix-musl-incompability.patch
4f7df148c71d3c0cabc985d2a724c560cbaed68c9183e942b7bcaa62136f40a6df63f2ae5779c01504f5a7fd4ee87f6214388140292c7a98b3bc66a6e3c29ea2  fix-cmake.patch"
